comments: Whiteside (POR) sets the pick in Mills's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact with DeRozan's (SAS) body during his driving shot attempt.
Hood (POR) is firming up in a picking position in Mills's (SAS) path when contact occurs and he absorbs the contact.
Prior to the inbound pass, DeRozan (SAS) briefly places an arm on Hood's (POR) hip.
DeRozan (SAS) jumps forward and delivers contact to Hood's (POR) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
White (SAS) rescreens and briefly delays Hood (POR) while setting the pick.
Whiteside (POR) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting DeRozan's (SAS) driving shot attempt.
During the screen, Aldridge (SAS) and Whiteside (POR) make marginal contact with one another as they move up the lane.
Whiteside (POR) sets the pick in White's (SAS) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Prior to the gather for the shot Hood (POR) extends his arm and makes contact with DeRozan's (SAS) face during the drive.
White (SAS) firms up in a picking position in Hood's (POR) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Whiteside (POR) makes incidental contact with DeRozan's (SAS) body after cleanly blocking his driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the foul called on DeRozan (SAS) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact with White's (SAS) body and removes his hand before White begins his upward shooting motion.
Mills (SAS) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
White (SAS) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
